Package it.unipr.barbato.Model.Message

Class NodesHandler

java.lang.Object
it.unipr.barbato.Model.Message.NodesHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
Handler, jakarta.jms.MessageListener
public class NodesHandler extends Object implements Handler, jakarta.jms.MessageListener
The NodesHandler class implements the Handler and MessageListener interfaces and represents a nodes handler in the distributed system. It take updated all nodes on the system status (the number of nodes and the process IDs of all node in the distributed system).
Author:
Vincenzo Barbato 345728
